1
00:00:02,680 --> 00:00:04,880
Fresh vegetables! Fresh vegetables!

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:09,250
Would you care for some vegetables?

3
00:00:10,420 --> 00:00:12,720
Fresh vegetables! Fresh vegetables!

4
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:17,640
Here, coconut pancakes.

5
00:00:19,280 --> 00:00:20,000
Master Rak.

6
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:21,440
What is it that brings you here?

7
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:23,760
I have come to make amends
with my dearest.

8
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:29,800
I bear you no grudge,

9
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:33,280
yet I could not fathom
why you addressed Miss Vila so sweetly.

10
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:35,480
"Vila."

11
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:40,280
I asked her to drop the title

12
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:41,880
and speak to me
as if we were no strangers.

13
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:44,040
That is to make sure

14
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:46,640
I see her solely as a sister.

15
00:00:48,300 --> 00:00:49,750
And when I said that

16
00:00:49,780 --> 00:00:51,880
Vila is already Sida,

17
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:55,800
how else could I tell a lady
forbidden to dance Khon?

18
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:59,280
If you or I

19
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,800
were born as ladies

20
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,880
and forbidden to dance Khon,

21
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:04,440
what a shame that would be.

22
00:01:08,100 --> 00:01:09,920
If you or I were a lady,

23
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,320
we might then love one another.

24
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:16,680
Now that we are both men,

25
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,960
are we not in love?

26
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,440
My dearest Saen.

27
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,680
I showed her kindness,

28
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:32,880
for I owed Phraya Dechanarong
a most gracious favor

29
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:35,600
when he saved your life.

30
00:01:37,140 --> 00:01:38,520
The day you were punished,

31
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:42,720
the Royal Master and Phraya Dechanarong

32
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:45,380
saved you from confinement,

33
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,600
as I had begged them to.

34
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,400
Master Rak...

35
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,800
Here, it is most delicious.

36
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:23,860
[Tanakorn Chuen-arom as Saen/Sand]

37
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:28,620
[Wacharathon Wongyai as Rak/Lucky]

38
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:32,740
[Worachai Areewong as Tan/Thank]

39
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:37,820
[Khitaphat Choothai as Chim/Charm]

40
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:41,420
[Kornkamon Supaseripap as Vila/ViVi]

41
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:45,680
[Rungtiva Sangngoen as Prink
Napat Seela as Rit/Ton]

42
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:49,260
[Chalisa Schaub as Kamala
Weeraachai Hatgovit as Phraya Banleng]

43
00:02:49,420 --> 00:02:53,620
[Nithiroj Simakamtorn as Phraya Dechanarong
Rattanachai Phakdirat as Khon Master]

44
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:04,440
Rit!

45
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:11,600
Rak?

46
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,920
Approach not.

47
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:15,400
If Father knows that you have seen me,

48
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,640
you shall be in trouble.

49
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:22,600
Where are you headed?

50
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,000
Are you bearing your child
to the physician?

51
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,320
I can pay for you.

52
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,600
Thank you, Rak.

53
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,080
Think nothing of it.

54
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,080
We are family.

55
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:04,010
[Tai Seng Apothecary]

56
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,000
Physician,

57
00:04:05,860 --> 00:04:07,560
please aid my mother.

58
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,240
She has been ailing for many days.

59
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,800
I am willing to work to pay off my debt.

60
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,520
I beg of you.

61
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,560
We made it clear that

62
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,000
should you have no money,

63
00:04:18,340 --> 00:04:19,640
we can offer you no aid.

64
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,920
This is all I have.

65
00:04:23,220 --> 00:04:24,280
I beg of you!

66
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,960
I have no money,

67
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,600
no prestige,

68
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,000
no right even to beg.

69
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:40,340
My mother is dying before their eyes,

70
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,080
yet they pay no heed.

71
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,400
Go to the physician, I pray.

72
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,640
The son of Phraya who fled from the house

73
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,000
has been reduced to a servant.

74
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,760
Though he was born with wealth,

75
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:03,030
it is his blood that shall come to his aid.

76
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,480
Unlike me,

77
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,480
who am bereft of all means.

78
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:14,080
Speak of this to no one.
Do you hear me?

79
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,360
It depends.

80
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:19,480
Some matters concern us not.

81
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,800
Am I wrong to look?

82
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:29,560
We agreed to the treatment.

83
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,200
Come, see your mother.

84
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,760
Is this true?!

85
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,560
Thank you, Heaven and Earth.

86
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,670
I thank you for your compassion.

87
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,640
Rak...

88
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,940
This is the training ground for men.

89
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,720
You are not meant to be here.

90
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:17,100
It is only the Khon training ground.

91
00:06:17,780 --> 00:06:19,440
How improper could it be?

92
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,880
I came only to watch.

93
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,080
Vila,

94
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,720
this place

95
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,040
is set aside for men to practice.

96
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,320
It is not proper for a lady
to practice Khon

97
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,560
in a place such as this.

98
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:39,040
I bear no ill intent.

99
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:41,040
I only wish to learn,

100
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:43,040
and for once to dance Khon.

101
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:48,760
Why is it forbidden for ladies
to dance Khon,

102
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:52,600
when so many roles in the story are female?

103
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:54,920
Ladies may dance only in plays.

104
00:06:56,420 --> 00:06:58,600
You possess a heart
for the performing arts.

105
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,760
I admire that.

106
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,360
I possess a heart for Khon.

107
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,360
Could you teach me...

108
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:10,080
please?

109
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:25,520
If you truly possess a heart
for the performing arts,

110
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:30,200
I shall teach you at your place.

111
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,920
Come here no more.

112
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,000
As you wish.

113
00:07:52,570 --> 00:07:54,280
Vila, do follow my lead.

114
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:55,520
Of course.

115
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,320
Am I correct?

116
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:05,800
Raise your elbow more.

117
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,520
Place your fingers before your lips.

118
00:08:13,540 --> 00:08:14,280
Well...

119
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,000
That is most right.

120
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,560
Rak,

121
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:21,800
your mind seems to be elsewhere.

122
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:24,840
Forgive me, Vila.

123
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,600
I was lost in thought.

124
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:31,880
Who occupied your thoughts?

125
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:33,920
Or...

126
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:35,600
are you weary?

127
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:39,840
I thought of no one.

128
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:44,240
I only recalled the movements
the Royal Master taught yesterday.

129
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:48,160
Though every time I look at you,

130
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,440
you seem so far away.

131
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:54,640
Speak to me with honesty.

132
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,360
Do you...

133
00:08:57,880 --> 00:09:00,040
belong to another?

134
00:09:01,180 --> 00:09:03,520
What prompted you to ask me this?

135
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:06,560
Each time you seem far away,

136
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,720
your eyes...

137
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,920
soften, as if recalling someone dear.

138
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:18,080
There is no such thing, Vila.

139
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:21,320
No lady has claimed my heart.

140
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,520
Is that truly so?

141
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,720
Are you deceiving me?

142
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,400
How could I do such a thing to my sister?

143
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,400
You spoke as though...

144
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,120
you desired a sister.

145
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,200
I would delight in that.

146
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:42,520
I only have a brother.

147
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:44,840
I wonder

148
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,160
what it would be like to have a sister.

149
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,360
Surely it pleases you greatly

150
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,880
that I am but your sister.

151
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,840
Be not troubled by it, Vila.

152
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,440
Shall we continue?

153
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,000
Follow my lead.

154
00:10:08,460 --> 00:10:09,320
As you wish.

155
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:37,240
It is time to inform them, would you agree?

156
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:41,360
I do not oppose it.

157
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,810
As you wish,

158
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,280
so shall it be.

159
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:52,640
Henceforth,
you are always welcome at my house,

160
00:10:52,980 --> 00:10:54,360
should you wish to come.

161
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:57,040
You need not ask for permission,

162
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,360
for soon...

163
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:03,280
you and Rak shall be joined as one.

164
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,640
You knew that

165
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:21,960
I had promised Vila to your brother,

166
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:25,440
yet he has brought shame upon our family.

167
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,960
Whispers arose on every side.

168
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:31,040
The woman with whom
he has entangled himself

169
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,800
is not of noble birth.

170
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,800
She is but a servant of loose conduct.

171
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:40,360
And they fled,
knowing neither the north nor the south.

172
00:11:43,660 --> 00:11:44,840
Do you know

173
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:49,640
that I have borne
this burden of shame to this very day?

174
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:53,280
I, a minister of noble station,

175
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:56,080
shall not endure such scorn.

176
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,320
They may not speak it to my face,

177
00:11:58,760 --> 00:12:02,600
yet such scorn is heard on every side.

178
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,040
Therefore, Rak,

179
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:11,560
it shall fall to you
to restore our family's honor.

180
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,600
Not your brother.

181
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:20,100
You must marry Vila,

182
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:23,560
that we may lay this to rest at last.

183
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:27,440
It is not merely love,

184
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:30,840
but our family's honor.

185
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:38,090
Think not that I shall suffer my other son

186
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:40,080
to commit the same error.

187
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,000
Love...

188
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,800
is not so lasting as honor.

189
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,290
Mark these words well.

190
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,360
Uncle,

191
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,840
I must speak my mind.

192
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:04,000
I cannot marry one
who holds me not in his heart.

193
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,040
And...

194
00:13:08,860 --> 00:13:10,320
I believe...

195
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:13,840
Rak's heart is already claimed.

196
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:19,080
Vila...

197
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,420
Speak no such thing to Phraya.

198
00:13:26,020 --> 00:13:27,120
It is impossible.

199
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:31,440
Rak remains always at Phranluang School,

200
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:35,240
and never involves himself with any woman.

201
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:39,520
What if...

202
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:44,440
I were mistaken?

203
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:51,000
Now, all of you,

204
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:55,960
has anyone seen my son, Rak,

205
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:59,260
entangled with any woman?

206
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,520
And what about you, Chim?

207
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:14,680
No, I have not, Your Excellency.

208
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:18,480
Master Rak
is ever at the Khon training place,

209
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:21,920
I see not a woman.

210
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,760
I must speak of this, Your Excellency.

211
00:14:42,660 --> 00:14:44,840
What may it be?

212
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:47,880
Most respectfully,

213
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:51,840
I have observed that
which is contrary to custom

214
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:55,080
between Rak and...

215
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:08,200
Phraya Dechanarong's daughter

216
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:11,640
at the training place.

217
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,360
This matter

218
00:15:18,380 --> 00:15:20,480
shall not leave this room.

219
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:26,560
The honor of Phraya Dechanarong
shall not be stained.

220
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:28,760
Rak,

221
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:32,200
you must marry Vila at once

222
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:35,680
to protect the honor of us all.

223
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,560
Can you dance for me, Saen?

224
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,900
Choose the verse of which
you are most proud.

225
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:25,840
At that

226
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:28,440
very instant,

227
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:35,560
the ten-headed giant,
descendant of the Sun,

228
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:41,440
beheld flames
soaring aloft with brilliance,

229
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:47,200
their scorching rays the fiercest of all.

230
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:51,640
The foundation of the palace
was set ablaze.

231
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:54,800
The great giant, struck with terror

232
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,200
and trembling,

233
00:16:58,400 --> 00:17:03,080
cried aloud for his two comely wives;

234
00:17:04,340 --> 00:17:06,280
the descendant of the Sun was thrown

235
00:17:07,740 --> 00:17:08,720
into chaos.

236
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:12,120
Carrying away his queen, Monto,

237
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:14,760
along with the radiant Akhkee,

238
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:17,560
he descended from
the gleaming crystal palace

239
00:17:19,040 --> 00:17:20,600
and swiftly

240
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:22,950
departed the city.

241
00:17:26,460 --> 00:17:27,360
Saen...

242
00:17:28,740 --> 00:17:29,760
Flee with me.

243
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:46,760
I am happy

244
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:50,000
when I see you as Thotsakan,

245
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:53,040
not a commoner,

246
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:56,040
not a servant bound to anyone.

247
00:18:01,060 --> 00:18:02,560
What if I no longer dance?

248
00:18:04,040 --> 00:18:05,560
Shall I still be bound to another?

249
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:16,800
You are worried,

250
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:21,960
for you do not wish to marry Miss Vila.
Is it so?

251
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:27,160
If you marry Miss Vila,

252
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:29,160
all shall be in order.

253
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:31,760
Saen

254
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:34,560
shall not be dragged down
into the same pit as you.

255
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:41,320
Worry not, Master Rak.

256
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,640
I shall speak of it no more

257
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:47,480
if you do what is yours to do,

258
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:49,680
marry her

259
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:52,360
and keep your distance from Saen.

260
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,480
And why should I?

261
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:58,200
Do you hold concern for me,

262
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:00,360
or for him?

263
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,720
I hold concern for all,

264
00:19:05,540 --> 00:19:06,560
and most of all

265
00:19:07,220 --> 00:19:09,930
for the one who must not be harmed again.

266
00:19:13,560 --> 00:19:15,080
Give it careful thought, Master Rak.

267
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,960
If you hesitate,

268
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:19,080
it will not be I...

269
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:20,760
who weeps.

270
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:46,400
Do you wish for us to make our escape?

271
00:19:49,420 --> 00:19:51,720
I shall do whatsoever my strength allows,

272
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:54,680
so that you may no longer live in fear.

273
00:19:58,300 --> 00:19:59,960
If I do not flee with you,

274
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,880
will you believe that...

275
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:06,060
I do not love you?

276
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,600
No.

277
00:20:16,420 --> 00:20:17,560
Whatever you do,

278
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:22,040
I know in my heart
that your love for me endures.

279
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:24,680
Though I...

280
00:20:26,540 --> 00:20:29,000
wish not that
you should suffer for my sake.

281
00:20:33,820 --> 00:20:35,960
I, too, wish you neither harm nor trouble.

282
00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:39,160
Soon,

283
00:20:40,120 --> 00:20:41,800
you may become a royal Khon dancer

284
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:45,760
just as your heart desires.

285
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:50,200
However, if I flee with you,

286
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,680
you may be forced to leave that

287
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,920
which is most dear to you.

288
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,440
The thing most dear to me...

289
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,840
is you, Master Rak.

290
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:14,160
Though I shall not oppose it.

291
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:19,560
I shall abide by your wish.

292
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:25,640
If there be another life,

293
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,760
let me belong to you and love you,

294
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,480
and may we know freedom from all obstacles.

295
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:54,440
May I...

296
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:56,840
touch you...

297
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,120
one last time?

298
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:12,600
♫Others adore flowers in the sun♫

299
00:22:12,780 --> 00:22:22,810
♫Yet we shall cross
the endless night as one,♫

300
00:22:22,840 --> 00:22:28,760
♫Together evermore♫
